quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  66,1,Ya eyyuhennebiyyu lime tuharrimu ma ehallellahu leke tebteÄÄḟy merdate ezvacike vallahu Äafurun rahÄḟymun
  66,2,Kad feredallahu lekum tehÄḟllete eymanikum vallahu mevlakum ve luvelÂṀalÄḟymulhakÄḟymu
  66,3,Ve iz eserrennebiyyu ila baÂṀdÄḟ ezvacihi hadiysen felemma nebbeet bihi ve ezharehullahu ÂṀaleyhi ÂṀarrefe baÂṀdahu ve aÂṀreda ÂṀanbaÂṀdÄḟn felemma nebbeeha bihi kalet men enbeeke haza kale nebbeeniyelÂṀaliymulhabiyru
  66,4,ÄḞn tetuba ilillahi fekad saÄat kulubukuma ve in tezahera ÂṀaleyhi feinnallahe huve mevlahu ve cibriylu ve salihulmu ÂṀminiyne velmelaiketu baÂṀde zalike zahiyrun
  66,5,ÂṀAsa rabbuhu in tallakakune en yubdilehu ezvacen hayren minkunne muslimatin muÂṀmunatin kanitatin taibatin ÂṀabidatin saihatin seyyibatin ve ebkaren
  66,6,Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu kuenfusekum ve ehliykum naren ve kuduhennasu velhÄḟcaretu ÂṀaleyha melaiketun ÄulazÄḟn Åidadin la yaÂṀsunallahe ma emerehum ve yefÂṀalune ma yuÂṀmerune
  66,7,Ya eyyuhelleziyne keferu la taÂṀtezirulyevme innema tuczevne ma kuntum taÂṀmelune
  66,8,Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu tubu ilellahi tevbeten nesuhan asa rabbukum en yukeffire ÂṀankum seyyiatikum ve yudhÄḟlekum cennatin tecriy min tahtihelÂṀenharu yevme la yuhzillahunnebiyye velleziyne amenu meÂṀahu nuruhum yesÂṀa beyne eydiyhim ve bieymanihim yekulune rabbena etmin lena nurena vaÄfir lena inneke ÂṀala kulli ÅeyÂṀin kadiyrun
  66,9,Ya eyyuhennebiyyu cahidilkuffare velmunafikÄḟyne vaÄluz ÂṀaleyhim ve meÂṀvahum cehennemu ve biÂṀselmasÄḟyru
  66,10,Dareballahu meselen lilleziyne keferumreete nuhÄḟn vemreete lutin kaneta tahte ÂṀabdeyni min ÂṀÄḟbadina salihayni fehanetahuma felem yuÄniya ÂṀanhuma minallahi ÅeyÂṀen ve kÄḟyledhulennare meÂṀaddahiliyne
  66,11,Ve da reballahu meselen lilleziyne amenumreete firÂṀavne iz kalet rabbibni liy ÂṀÄḟndeke beyten fiylcenneti ve necciniy min firÂṀavne ve ÂṀamelihi ve necciniy minelkavmizzalimiyne
  66,12,Ve meryemebte ÂṀÄḟmranelletiy ahsanet ferceha fenefahna fiyhi min ruhÄḟna ve saddekat bikelimati rabbiha ve kutubihi ve kanet minelkanitÄḟyne